data.description: This is it!  Your new home awaits you.  Picture yourself sitting out back on your patio in the mornings while the sun rises over you or relax in the afternoons when the sun begins to fall.  Or can I suggest the warmth of the three seasons room that is fully enclosed.  You can even cozy up to the wood burning fireplace while making memories with family and friends in this nearly 2800sqft property.  This home features 4 total bedrooms and 3 full bathrooms including its own “in law” suite with a separate kitchen, living, and laundry area.  Nestled in Delmar, Maryland near the Delaware line, this home is located within a short distance to Route 50 that can take you east to the beach or west across the bridge.  Enjoy the shopping that Salisbury offers only 10 miles away, the Salisbury Zoological Park, Tidal Health facilities including its renowned hospital, or fishing in nearby waterways.  Your new chapter in your life begins here and after all...You deserve it!
